quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  57,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  57,1,jo makhlooq asmano aur zameen mein hai khuda ki tasbeeh karti hai. aur woh ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  57,2,asmano aur zameen ki badshahi isi ki hai. ( wohi ) zindah karta aur maarta hai. aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  57,3,woh ( sab se ) pehla aur ( sab se ) pichla aur ( apni qudraton se sab par ) zahir aur ( apni zaat se ) posheeda hai aur woh tamam cheezon ko jaanta hai
  57,4,wohi hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay din mein pedakiya phir arsh par ja thehra. jo cheez zameen mein daakhil hoti aur jo is se nikalti hai aur jo aasman se utartee aur jo is ki taraf chadhti hai sab is ko maloom hai. aur tum jahan kahin ho woh tumahray sath hai. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is ko dekh raha hai
  57,5,asmano aur zameen ki badshahi isi ki hai. aur sab umoor isi ki taraf rujoo hotay hain
  57,6,raat ko din mein daakhil karta aur din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai. aur woh dilon ke bheidoon taq se waaqif hai
  57,7,to ) khuda par aur is ke rasool par imaan lao aur jis ( maal ) mein is ne tum ko ( apna ) naib banaya hai is mein se kharch karo. jo log tum mein se imaan laaye aur ( maal ) kharch karte rahay un ke liye bara sawab hai
  57,8,aur tum kaisay log ho ke khuda par imaan nahi laatay. halaank ( is ke ) paighambar tumhe bulaa rahay hain ke apne perwar-digaar par imaan lao aur agar tum ko bawar ho to woh tum se ( is ka ) ehad bhi le chuka hai
  57,9,wohi to hai jo apne bande par wazeh ( اul matalib ) ayatain nazil karta hai taakay tum ko andheron mein se nikaal kar roshni mein laaye. be shak khuda tum par nihayat shafqat karne wala ( aur ) meharban hai
  57,10,aur tum kokiya howa hai ke khuda ke raste mein kharch nahi karte halaank asmano aur zameen ki waarsat khuda hi ki hai. jis shakhs ne tum mein se fatah ( mecca ) se pehlay kharchkiya aur larai ki woh ( aur jis ne yeh kaam peechay kiye woh ) barabar nahi. un ka darja un logon se kahin barh kar hai jinhon ne baad mein kharch ( amwal ) aur ( kufar se ) jehaad o qitaal kiya. aur khuda ne sab se ( sawab ) naik ( ka ) wada tokiya hai. aur jo kaam tum karte ho khuda un se waaqif hai
  57,11,kon hai jo khuda ko ( niyat ) naik ( aur khuloos se ) qarz day to woh is ko is se dugna kere aur is ke liye izzat ka sila ( yani jannat ) hai
  57,12,jis din tum momin mardon aur momin aurton ko dekho ge ke un ( ke imaan ) ka noor un ke agay agay aur dahni taraf chal raha hai ( to un se kaha jaye ga ke ) tum ko basharat ho ( ke aaj tumahray liye ) baagh hain jin ke taley nehrain beh rahi hain un mein hamesha raho ge. yahi barri kamyabi hai
  57,13,uss din munhafiq mard aur munhafiq aurtain mominoun se kahin ge ke hamari taraf se ( shafqat ) kijiye ke hum bhi tumahray noor se roshni haasil karen. to un se kaha jaye ga ke peechay ko lout jao aur ( wahan ) noor talaash karo. phir un ke beech mein aik deewar khari kar di jaye gi. jis mein aik darwaaza hoga jo is ki janib androoni hai is mein to rehmat hai aur jo janib bairooni hai is taraf azaab ( o azziyat )
  57,14,to munhafiq log mominoun se kahin ge kekiya hum ( duniya mein ) tumahray sath nah they woh kahin ge kyun nahi they. lekin tum ne khud apne tain bulaa mein dala aur ( hamaray haq mein hawadis ke ) munhtazir rahay aur ( islam mein ) shakkiya aur ( laa-ta-il ) aarzouon ne tum ko dhoka diya yahan taq ke khuda ka hukum aa pouncha aur khuda ke baray mein tum ko ( shetan ) daga baaz dagha deta raha
  57,15,to aaj tum se muawza nahi liya jaye ga aur nah ( woh ) kafiroon hi se ( qubool kiya jaye ga ) tum sab ka thikana dozakh hai. ( ke ) wohi tumahray Laiq hai aur woh buri jagah hai
  57,16,kiya abhi taq mominoun ke liye is ka waqt nahi aaya ke khuda ki yaad karne ke waqt aur ( quran ) jo ( khuday-e ) brhq ( ki taraf ) se nazil howa hai is ke suneney ke waqt un ke dil naram ho jaien aur woh un logon ki taraf nah ho jaien jin ko ( un se ) pehlay kitaaben di gayi theen. phir un par Zaman taweel guzar gaya to un ke dil sakht hogaye. aur un mein se aksar nafarman hain
  57,17,jaan rakho ke khuda hi zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad zindah karta hai. hum ne apni nishanain tum se khol khol kar bayan kar di hain taakay tum samjhoo
  57,18,jo log khairaat karne walay hain mard bhi aur aurtain bhi. aur khuda ko ( niyat ) naik ( aur khuloos se ) qarz dete hain un ko dochnd adakiya jaye ga aur un ke liye izzat ka sila hai
  57,19,aur jo log khuda aur is ke payghambaroon par imaan laaye yahi apne perwar-digaar ke nazdeek Seddiq aur shaheed hain. un ke liye un ( ke aamaal ) ka sila hoga. aur un ( ke imaan ) ki roshni. aur jin logon ne kufarkiya aur hamari aayton ko jhtlaya wohi ahal dozakh hain
  57,20,jaan rakho ke duniya ki zindagi mehez khail aur tamasha aur zeenat ( vaaraysh ) aur tumahray aapas mein fakhr ( vstaysh ) aur maal o aulaad ki aik dosray se ziyada talab ( o khawhish ) hai ( is ki misaal aisi hai ) jaisay barish ke ( is se khaiti ugti aur ) kisanon ko khaiti bhali lagti hai phir woh khoob zor par aati hai phir ( ae dekhnay walay ) to is ko daikhta hai ke ( pick kar ) zard par jati hai phir choora choora hojati hai aur akhirat mein ( kafiroon ke liye ) azaab shadeed aur ( mominoun ke liye ) khuda ki taraf se bakhshish aur khushnodi hai. aur duniya ki zindagi to mata fraib hai
  57,21,( Bandoo ) apne perwar-digaar ki bakhshish ki taraf aur jannat ki ( taraf ) jis ka arz aasman aur zameen ke arz ka sa hai. aur jo un logon ke liye tayyar ki gayi hai jo khuda par aur is ke payghambaroon par imaan laaye hain lapko. yeh khuda ka fazl hai jisay chahay ataa farmaiye. aur khuda barray fazl ka maalik hai
  57,22,koi museebat malik par aur khud tum par nahi padtee magar peshtar is ke ke hum is ko peda karen aik kitaab mein ( likhi hui ) hai. ( aur ) yeh ( kaam ) khuda ko aasaan hai
  57,23,taakay jo ( matlab ) tum se faut hogaya ho is ka gham nah khaya karo aur jo tum ko is ne diya ho is par itrayea nah karo. aur khuda kisi itranay aur shekhi bigharnay walay ko dost nahi rakhta
  57,24,jo khud bhi bukhal karen aur logon ko bhi bukhal skhayin aur jo shakhs rogrdani kere to khuda bhi be parwa ( aur ) wohi sazawar hamd ( وثنا ) hai
  57,25,hum ne apne payghambaroon ko khuli nishanain day kar bheja. aur unn par kitaaben nazil kee aur traazo ( yani qawaid Adal ) taakay log insaaf par qaim rahen. aur loha pedakiya is mein ( aslah ٴ jung ke lehaaz se ) khatrah bhi shadeed hai. aur logon ke liye faiday bhi hain aur is liye ke jo log ban dekhe khuda aur is ke payghambaroon ki madad karte hain khuda un ko maloom kere. be shak khuda quwwat ( aur ) ghalib hai
  57,26,aur hum ne Nooh aur ibrahim ko ( paighambar bana kar ) bheja aur un ki aulaad mein paigambri aur kitaab ( ke silsilay ) ko ( vqtan fawaqtan jari ) rakha to baaz to un mein se hadaayat par hain. aur aksar un mein se kharij az itaat hain
  57,27,phir un ke peechay unhi ke qadmon par ( aur ) paighambar beje aur un ke peechay maryam ke betay eesa ko bheja aur un ko injeel inayat ki. aur jin logon ne un ki pairwi ki un ke dilon mein shafqat aur meharbani daal di. aur lazat se kinara kashi ki to unhon ne khud aik nai baat nikaal li hum ne un ko is ka hukum nahi diya tha magar ( unhon ne apne khayaal mein ) khuda ki khushnodi haasil karne ke liye ( aap hi aisa karliya tha ) phir jaissa is ko نباہنا chahiye tha nibaah bhi nah sakay. pas jo log un mein se imaan laaye un ko hum ne un ka ajar diya aur un mein bohat se nafarman hain
  57,28,momino! khuda se daro aur is ke paighambar par imaan lao woh tumhe apni rehmat se dugna ajar ataa farmaiye ga aur tumahray liye roshni kardey ga jis mein chalo ge aur tum ko bakhash day ga. aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  57,29,( yeh baatein ) is liye ( bayan ki gayi hain ) ke ahal kitaab jaan len ke woh khuda ke fazl par kuch bhi qudrat nahi rakhtay. aur yeh ke fazl khuda hi ke haath hai jis ko chahta hai deta hai aur khuda barray fazl ka maalik hai
